com.here.android.mpa.common

Class ViewObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.common.ViewObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MapObject, MapProxyObject, StreetLevelObject, StreetLevelProxyObject

    public abstract class ViewObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the base class implementation for all objects that are selectable from a view.

    Selectable objects are featured on these views:

    • MapFragment
    • MapView
